						<span style="display:block; text-indent:2em;">您好！您的朋友{fullname}在<a href='http://hr.ofweek.com'>OFweek人才网</a>看到{companyname}在招聘<a href='http://hr.ofweek.com/jobs/jobs-show-{id}.html'>{jobs_name}</a>。觉得比较适合你，现将此职位推荐给您，详情如下：</span></span></td>
		</tr>
		<tr>
		<td style="padding:5px 20px 0;line-height:25px; ">
